tidy: tidy (Utility to help clean up your Web pages)
tidy:
tidy: HTML Tidy is a free utility to automatically fix mistakes in HTML,
tidy: and tidy up sloppy editing into nicely laid out markup.  It also
tidy: works great on the hard-to-read markup generated by specialized HTML
tidy: editors and conversion tools, and can bring to your attention things
tidy: that you need to work on yourself.
